English Translation

I’ll be the place where you can
Lay down your weary head
I’ll be by your side when everything’s just
Too much to handle, yet you can’t give up

I love Seoul Seoul I’ll give you hope
Seoul Seoul I’ll look deep into your eyes
Walk to your pace side by side
And put a smile on your face
I love Seoul Seoul I’ll be worthy of your love
Seoul Seoul I’ll be worth your time singing
I’ll be that someone

Oh Seoul, I’m here always
Ready to make you happy, just see
Oh Seoul, I’m here for you
With my ears, eyes, and arms wide open
